        "CodeBlock"
      ],
      "name": "Code 1",
      "chunk_text": "- [ ] Provenance; track data lineage; forbid orphaned metadata\n- [ ] Neutrality; use domain-agnostic keys; forbid sector-specific fields\n- [ ] Consistency; apply uniform naming; forbid arbitrary conventions\n- [ ] Versioning; track generation timestamps; forbid undated artifacts\n- [ ] Documentation; explain all fields; forbid undocumented properties",
