      "@type": "Table",
      "labels": [
        "Table"
      ],
      "name": "Table 4",
      "chunk_text": "| Legacy Value           | Normalized Value | Client Behavior                                              |\n|------------------------|------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|\n| `\"document-structure\"` | `\"document\"`     | Canvas normalizes on load, uses `\"document\"` internally      |\n| `\"property\"`           | `\"schema\"`       | Canvas normalizes on load, treats as raw schema layer        |",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Legacy Value           | Normalized Value | Client Behavior                                              |\n|------------------------|------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|\n| `\"document-structure\"` | `\"document\"`     | Canvas normalizes on load, uses `\"document\"` internally      |\n| `\"property\"`           | `\"schema\"`       | Canvas normalizes on load, treats as raw schema layer        |",
        "order": 4
      },
