      "name": "Table 7",
      "chunk_text": "| Context               | Intent                        | Directive                                                                                   | Module/Component          | Function/Method      | Input                     | Output                | Decision Logic                          |\n|-----------------------|-------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------|----------------------|---------------------------|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------|\n| Layer Extraction      | Isolate metadata subset       | - [ ] Navigate to `metadata.layers` in schema-config; extract; forbid partial extraction    | CLI handler               | `extract_layers`     | sch",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Context               | Intent                        | Directive                                                                                   | Module/Component          | Function/Method      | Input                     | Output                | Decision Logic                          |\n|-----------------------|-------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------|----------------------|---------------------------|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------|\n| Layer Extraction      | Isolate metadata subset       | - [ ] Navigate to `metadata.layers` in schema-config; extract; forbid partial extraction    | CLI handler               | `extract_layers`     | schema-config object      | layers dict           | dict key access with validation         |\n| Pretty Printing       | Format for readability        | - [ ] Use JSON.dumps with indent=2; forbid minified output                                  | CLI handler               | `print_layers`       | layers dict               | formatted string      | json.dumps(..., indent=2)               |",
        "order": 7
