    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-metadata-document:table:568:5",
      "@type": "Table",
      "labels": [
        "Table"
      ],
      "name": "Table 5",
      "chunk_text": "| Context               | Intent                        | Directive                                                                                   | Module/Component          | Function/Method          | Input                     | Output                | Decision Logic                          |\n|-----------------------|-------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------|--------------------------|---------------------------|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------|\n| Fragment Stripping    | Extract base document path    | - [ ] Remove `#Lx-Ly` suffix; return base path; forbid double fragments                     | `documentMetadata`        | `stripFragment`   ",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Context               | Intent                        | Directive                                                                                   | Module/Component          | Function/Method          | Input                     | Output                | Decision Logic                          |\n|-----------------------|-------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------|--------------------------|---------------------------|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------|\n| Fragment Stripping    | Extract base document path    | - [ ] Remove `#Lx-Ly` suffix; return base path; forbid double fragments                     | `documentMetadata`        | `stripFragment`          | documentPath string       | base path string      | regex replace `/#L\\d+-\\d+$/` with empty |\n| Fallback Resolution   | Find effective path           | - [ ] Try documentPath, then codebaseRelPath, then codebasePath; forbid undefined return    | `documentMetadata`        | `resolveDocumentPath`    | node metadata object      | path string or null   | sequential field access with null checks|\n| Line Range Extraction | Get source line span          | - [ ] Read lineStart/lineEnd; validate range; forbid inverted ranges                         | `documentMetadata`        | `resolveLineRange`       | node metadata object      | {start, end} or null  | validate start <= end, return object    |",
        "order": 5
      },
