        "sourcePath": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph/docs/documents/knowgrph-metadata-document.md",
        "codebasePath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-metadata-document.md#L576",
        "lineStart": 576,
        "lineEnd": 576,
        "sourceSha256": "0095d2179a3a1bb1aa717c01ef86f17b338d1749f05b23d8040a84fda0ddf863"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-metadata-document:table:578:2",
      "@type": "Table",
      "labels": [
        "Table"
      ],
      "name": "Table 2",
      "chunk_text": "| Context              | Intent                          | Directive                                                                                   |\n|----------------------|---------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n| Graph Metadata       | Ensure completeness             | - [ ] Validate `graphId`, `generatedAt`, `agenticRagSchema` presence; forbid missing core fields |\n| Schema-Config Metadata | Ensure alignment              | - [ ] Verify `agenticRagSchema` matches graph; validate `layersFromGraph` structure; forbid mismatched schemas |\n| Provenance Metadata  | Ensure resolvability            | - [ ] Validate at least one of `documentPath`/`codebaseRelPath` present; forbid orphaned nodes |",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Context              | Intent                          | Directive                                                                                   |\n|----------------------|---------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n| Graph Metadata       | Ensure completeness             | - [ ] Validate `graphId`, `generatedAt`, `agenticRagSchema` presence; forbid missing core fields |\n| Schema-Config Metadata | Ensure alignment              | - [ ] Verify `agenticRagSchema` matches graph; validate `layersFromGraph` structure; forbid mismatched schemas |\n| Provenance Metadata  | Ensure resolvability            | - [ ] Validate at least one of `documentPath`/`codebaseRelPath` present; forbid orphaned nodes |",
        "order": 2
      },
      "metadata": {
