    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-metadata-document:table:588:2",
      "@type": "Table",
      "labels": [
        "Table"
      ],
      "name": "Table 2",
      "chunk_text": "| Context              | Status | Directive                                                                                   |\n|----------------------|--------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n| Graph Core Fields    | ☐      | - [ ] All graphs have `graphId`, `generatedAt`, `agenticRagSchema`; forbid partial metadata |\n| Layer Hints          | ☐      | - [ ] Graphs with semantic layers have `metadata.layers.semantic`; forbid undocumented hints |\n| Schema Alignment     | ☐      | - [ ] Schema-configs mirror graph `agenticRagSchema`; forbid mismatched IRIs                |",
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "| Context              | Status | Directive                                                                                   |\n|----------------------|--------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n| Graph Core Fields    | ☐      | - [ ] All graphs have `graphId`, `generatedAt`, `agenticRagSchema`; forbid partial metadata |\n| Layer Hints          | ☐      | - [ ] Graphs with semantic layers have `metadata.layers.semantic`; forbid undocumented hints |\n| Schema Alignment     | ☐      | - [ ] Schema-configs mirror graph `agenticRagSchema`; forbid mismatched IRIs                |",
        "order": 2
